WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:48.800 --> 00:00:50.600
Press the A button after jumping

00:00:50.600 --> 00:00:54.000
to launch a Homing Attack that zeroes in on enemies.

00:00:56.700 --> 00:00:59.800
Hold down the X button for a boost of speed.

00:00:59.800 --> 00:01:02.300
Once the Boost Gauge on the lower-left is empty,

00:01:02.300 --> 00:01:04.300
you can no longer use boost.

00:01:04.300 --> 00:01:08.000
Defeat enemies and collect Rings to refill the boost gauge.

00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:38.800
Use the left stick to move between the left and right rails while grinding.

